data.description: You won't want to miss this opportunity!! This classic home boasts large and open bedrooms and an extra half bath in one of them. Bedrooms are carpeted, but the rest of the house has beautiful wood flooring that was added when the house was renovated about 5 years ago. You'll love the big windows, open living area, gas stove, and bonus areas that can be used as dining, office, entry, den. SO many options!! It's not easy to find one of these classic houses that has been so well taken care of. Owner occupied. Please make an appointment to see.
